languages.text:
"The Cognisance Fleet will be //glad//alternative unavailable// to accept:
1) any samples of sacred technology;
2) samples of profane xenotech;
3) miscellaneous items.
Reminder: storage, study, and/or disposal of the aforementioned objects with the exception of 3) miscellaneous items is the preferential right of the Adeptus Mechanicus."

